          "date": "2014-05-14 10:30:53.000000000",
          "tz": 120
        },
        "subject": "LU-5060 zfs: execution fails due to fix lib. name libzfs.so.1",
        "message": "LU-5060 zfs: execution fails due to fix lib. name libzfs.so.1\n\nExecuting mkfs.lustre with --backfstype=zfs seeks for\nlibzfs.so.1 via handle_libzfs = dlopen(\"libzfs.so.1\", RTLD_LAZY);\nThe current version of ZFS 0.6.2-274_g2c33b91 compiles version\nlibzfs.so.2.0.0 and create links libzfs.so -> libzfs.so.2.0.0,\nlibzfs.so.2 -> libzfs.so.2.0.0 which will not be found by\nthe fix library name provided to dlopen.\n\nSigned-off-by: Thomas Stibor <thomas@stibor.net>\nChange-Id: Ic2005ed94b1f4a7a8496bd7ee07af6ec7d62e3af\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
